              I'm a detail-oriented designer and developer with strong analytical abilities.
              I'm passionate about solving real-world problems for real people
              by understanding every part of the problem and solution. I love learning
              about design, data, AI, emerging technologies, and art.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
              I have a BA in Cognitive Science from UC Berkeley, and a certificate in
              Full Stack Web Development from the UC Berkeley Extension. I discovered
              my passion for the intersection of psychology, design, and technology towards the end of my
              four years at Cal and enrolled in the Full Stack program at the Extension
              soon after graduating. I'm currently looking for roles in frontend
